title: Iron Maiden Madison Square Garden Tickets: QueenBeeTickets.com Reduces Prices on Iron Maiden Concert Tickets for MSG Show in New York on March 30, 2016
text:
By: ABNewswire - Press Release Distribution Service October 10, 2015 at 02:00 AM EDT Iron Maiden Madison Square Garden Tickets: QueenBeeTickets.com Reduces Prices on Iron Maiden Concert Tickets for MSG Show in New York on March 30, 2016 Iron Maiden Madison Square Garden Tickets at QueenBeeTickets.com Iron Maiden Madison Square Garden tickets become available to the general public beginning October 10 at 10:00 am as part of the newly-announced Book of Souls World Tour. To the delight of fans, trusted provider QueenBeeTickets.com has reduced its prices on Iron Maiden concert tickets for the show at MSG in New York. This live event is scheduled for March 30, 2016, and seats are expected to sell quickly. 
The band will travel to various worldwide locations next year during “The Book of Souls Tour” that will promote the album of the same name. U.S. dates begin on February 24 and end on April 15. During that time, the band will visit Ft. Lauderdale, Tulsa, Las Vegas, Detroit, Chicago, New York, Tacoma, Denver and Los Angeles. Iron Maiden Madison Square Garden tickets will be among those selling the quickest. 
Visit QueenBeeTickets.com to browse the inventory of Iron Maiden tickets at reduced prices. 
Heavy metal fans are excited about next year’s shows, and they have good reason to feel this way. The musicians are planning phenomenal events for their fans, and audiences are in for quite a treat when they obtain seats for a 2016 live concert. Even though the set list has not yet been worked out, it is certain that the band will entertain audiences with great music that will include new material. 
With so many heavy metal fans residing in and near The Big Apple, there is no doubt that Iron Maiden concert tickets for MSG in New York will be quite popular and may sell out within a very short period of time. Seats for the March 30 show go on sale to the general public on October 10, and presales have been scheduled for October 6, 8 and 9 at 10:00 A.M. CST. 
Besides U.S. shows, the entertainers also intend to announce Canadian events, and they will travel outside North America as well. Bruce Dickinson of the group has stated that they are planning a spectacular show. Fans will certainly want to make every effort to obtain good seats for one of next year’s live events, and New Yorkers will want to be quick in obtaining Iron Maiden Madison Square Garden tickets for a show that is certain to book solid in record time. 
QueenBeeTickets.com provides concertgoers with the opportunity to obtain Iron Maiden concert tickets for MSG in New York at great prices that are sure to please those on a limited entertainment budget. The popular ticket exchange has many good seats available for enthusiastic music fans to obtain quickly and easily.
